00:50:22,561 --> 00:50:26,565
Even if we're not soul mates,
it's a kind of love.

776
00:50:26,648 --> 00:50:32,028
And it keeps her eyes somewhere else,
so the rest I can give to you.

777
00:50:32,112 --> 00:50:35,031
